<!-- Game Description Table -->

<table class="tablestyle" id="table14" cellspacing="4" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td class="sectional">

<!-- Game Description Header -->
		
		<table class="headertable" id="table15" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="2">
			<tr>
				<td class="headercell">
				<img border="0" src="../../../images/headers/gamedes.jpg" width="240" height="33"></td>
			</tr>
		</table>

<!-- Game Description Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
			<br>Pachamama is the leader of a democratic movement and is returning to her country Meruza for an election. Naturally the tyrannical dictator will want to prevent her at all costs. A bomb is planted on the plane that she is travelling.
			<br><br>On board the plane are several other people such as journalists who want to interview her. Halfway, the plane explodes and crashes into Aconcagua. There are some survivors and you need to guide them down the mountain and escape the Meruzian soldiers who are out to complete their task of killing Pachamama and all other survivors.
			<br><br>CAST: 
			<br>- 1) Pachamama (leader of the democratic movement of Meruza): She’s a strong and determined woman, heading the movement to free Meruza from the tyranny of the pitiless leader. Her dedication to this mission is inspiring to all others.
			<br>- 2) Katon (Japanese journalist): He’s a Japanese journalist on board of the airplane, trying to cover the story of Pachamama. The death of his friend and co worker in the plane crash provides him strength to carry on. Because of the skills he acquired as a former alpinist, his contribution to the survival of the team is essential.
			<br>- 3) Steve (engenier from usa): A talented engineer and a resourceful helping hand, Steve often shows signs of anxiety and panic. But the harsh environment and sheer will to live end up revealing his greatest traits.
			<br>- 4) Julia (American journalist): Presenting herself as a journalist, Julia comes from the United States in pursuit of the story about the expected coup d’état. Her sweet looks contrast with the true nature of her identity.
			<br>- 5) Lopez: The last member to join the group, Lopez appears to be another survivor from the crash. He is a strongly built native who relies on his muscular strength to displace large and heavy objects.			
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Manufacturer's description:</u><br>
                  <br>Best South America "Aconcagua" five people survived the crashed airliner, and a mysterious armed group to combat the threat of descent for natural living easy adventure game with the cursor. By switching the operation well with five different special skills to clear the trap planted on the stage, aim for the descent.
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Features:</u><br>
			<ul><li>Third person perspective.</li>
			<li>3D graphics</li>
			<li>Cartoon graphics</li>			
			<li>Counter-terrorist theme.</li></ul>
</td>

	</tr>
	</table>
	       	</td>
     </tr>
</table>  

